parameters: You can change the Camera Perspective Settings
into Normal, Isometric and First Person View.
The NPC to change the settings is near the weapon shop.
You can also your Left Mouse Button to interact with
entrances, doors, chests, enemies and etc.
So if you're having a hard time to press Spacebar to enter
doors and entrances. You can just click them with the LMB.
There are wild enemies to try out the battle system.
Mounts (Ships and Dragon?), and castles out there.
Be sure to explore em all and have fun!
